Class twbotwatchtk

java.lang.Object
  twcore.bots.TWBotExtension
      twcore.bots.twbot.twbotwatchtk

public class twbotwatchtk
extends TWBotExtension

This module lets the bot monitor the teamkills, and take action of spec for a x amount of minutes if, depending on the variables, a certain amount of teamkills are made.
